title: Printing to Canon PIXMA MG3650S - "Cannot Find Supported Printer" message
content: Trying to connect to my new Canon MG3650S inkjet via MiFi/home network using the Canon Printer Service on my Pixel.  Entered the printer's IP address when prompted, but got a "Cannot find supported printer at this address" message.  Tried it a few times with the same result.  Looking for suggestions on how to fix
